{"word":"H833 - אָשַׁר - ʼâshar - aw-shar' - Bless","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אָשַׁר</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼâshar"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>aw-shar'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Bless"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"நட, பாக்கியவதி என்று சொல் நடத்து ஆதரி,"},{"paragraph":"பாக்கியவான் என்று வாழ்த்து, பாக்கியவானாயிரு. வாழ்த்து - வினைச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to go straight, to walk, to go on, to advance, to make progress"},{"paragraph":"a) (Qal) to go straight on, to make progress"},{"paragraph":"b) (Piel)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to go straight on, to advance"},{"paragraph":"2) to lead on (causative)"},{"paragraph":"3) to set right, to righten"},{"paragraph":"4) to pronounce happy, to call blessed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"c) (Pual)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"1) to be advanced, to be led on"},{"paragraph":"2) to be made happy, to be blessed"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; to <i>be straight</i> (used in the widest sense, especially to <i>be level</i>, <i>right</i>, <i>happy</i>); figuratively to <i>go forward</i>, <i>be honest</i>, <i>prosper: - </i>(call, be) bless (-ed, happy), go, guide, lead, relieve."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H833 - אָשַׁר - ʼâshar - aw-shar'/833\">H833</a>, <a href=\"#/H835 - אֶשֶׁר - ʼesher - eh'-sher/835\">H835</a>, <a href=\"#/H836 - אָשֵׁר - ʼÂshêr - aw-share'/836\">H836</a>, <a href=\"#/H837 - אֹשֶׁר - ʼôsher - o'-sher/837\">H837</a>, <a href=\"#/H838 - אָשֻׁר - ʼâshur - aw-shoor'/838\">H838</a>, <a href=\"#/H839 - אֲשֻׁר - ʼăshur - ash-oor'/839\">H839</a>, <a href=\"#/H8391 - תְּאַשּׁוּר - tᵉʼashshûwr - teh-ash-shoor'/8391\">H8391</a>, <a href=\"#/H842 - אֲשֵׁרָה - ʼăshêrâh - ash-ay-raw'/842\">H842</a>, <a href=\"#/H843 - אָשֵׁרִי - ʼÂshêrîy - aw-shay-ree'/843\">H843</a>"}]}